Rem 3、发送smtp邮件
Rem 功能：发送smtp邮件
Rem 入参：server: 邮件服务器IP  port: 邮件服务器端口 passport: 邮箱 password: 邮箱密码 sendAddr: 接收邮箱，多个邮箱用分号隔开 title: 标题 content: 正文 attachment: 附件 ssl: 是否ssl
Rem 出参：无

Function SendMailSMTP(server,port,passport,password,sendAddr,title,content,attachment,ssl)
	If Type(sendAddr) = "string"
		sendAddr = Split(sendAddr,";")
	End If
	For Each addr In sendAddr
	   Rem 发送异常重试2次
		For idx=0 To 3
			Try
				Mail.Send(server,passport,password,addr,title,content,attachment,port,ssl)
				Break
			Catch ex
				Log.Warn("邮件发送异常:"&CStr(ex))
			End Try
			Delay(3000)
		Next
	Next
End Function


